  "text": "Chitosan and its derivatives are known as a swollen bead support for preparation of immobilized enzyme [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Chitosan has very good biocompatibility, low toxicity, chemically inert and high hydrophilicity [CITATION_3] .",
